  "body": [
    "Bhai Avtar Singh Ji was from the Khar suburb of Mumbai (formerly known as Bombay). His Kirtan was well appreciated by many of the popular film stars in Bollywood and he performed Kirtan at many of their homes and weddings. Bhai Avtar Singh Ji passed away on 16th August 2011 in Southall, United Kingdom. His son, Bhai Ravinder Singh has also followed in his footsteps. At the moment we do not have any other information regarding Bhai Avtar Singh Ji. If anyone has more information or recordings of Bhai Avtar Singh Ji to share, please contact us."
